# AI-Powered Fabric Sourcing Assistant

## 🚀 Overview
This project is a voice-enabled web application that converts speech into structured fabric order details using AI.

---

## ✨ Features
- 🎤 Voice-to-text using Web Speech API  
- 🤖 AI-based extraction using LLM  
- 📝 Auto form filling  
- ✏️ Editable fields  
- 📄 Summary page  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Frontend: HTML, JavaScript  
- Backend: Flask (Python)  
- AI: OpenAI LLM  

---

## ▶️ How to Run

### 1. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install flask openai
